casebody.data:
Dixon, Admr., Appellant, v. General Motors Corporation, Appellee.

[Cite as Dixon v. Gen. Motors Corp. (1995), 74 Ohio St.3d 1211.]

(No. 94-1557 Submitted October 25, 1995 at the Van Wert Session Decided November 29, 1995.) Williams, Jilek, Lafferty & Gallagher Co., L.P.A., Robert M. Scott and Susan M. Mesner, for appellant. Jones, Day, Reavis & Pogue, James E. Young, Anne Owings Ford and Karen Kazel Poulos, for appellee.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
